{"tid":1276791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我發夢見到香港愈黎愈似V個世界","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T02:55:32.000Z","uid":15209,"like":166,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c910c6bd208df7136adae76e647a5cc22ad111f","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始<br />\n我覺得香港愈黎愈似 V 個世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0K17b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0K17b.jpg&h=73e246e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特別是近10幾年, 香港政權逐步逐步挑戰香港人嘅底線<br />\n由2003年廿三條開始，香港電視牌照風波，高鐵工程，第三條跑道，港珠澳大橋，國民教育，ＤＱ議員，，雨傘運動，魚蛋革命，鉛水事件，新界東北發展，中環海濱割地，沙中線醜聞。。。。。。。我數唔落去了<br />\n<br />\nＶ個世界，係極權統治下，係一個絕望無助嘅世界，充滿白色恐怖嘅世界，警察淪為政治工具，加上種種被嚴重鈕曲嘅價值觀，係一個典型嘅　Dystonia。係一個冇人想要嘅世界。<br />\n<br />\n同現時嘅香港，我可以話係無分別。<br />\n<br />\n慶幸嘅係Ｖ世界裡面嘅人民覺醒，成功推倒一個腐敗嘅政權<br />\n我想講香港都好慶幸有一班辛辛學子喚醒左一班＂不了要返工＂，＂好攰咪搞＂，＂政治關我撚事＂嘅香港人，將 ６９，６１２，６１９，７１上演。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話Ｖ世界裡面多得Ｖ嘅出現，香港尚欠一個Ｖ<br />\n其實係香港，Ｖ早就出現了<br />\n佢係你嘅親人，佢係你嘅朋友，佢亦都係你嘅同事<br />\n佢係同你一齊發夢嘅每一位<br />\n佢係我地任何一個<br />\n<br />\n係Ｖ呢個咁黑暗嘅世界都有一絲曙光<br />\n我相信香港都有<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Behind this mask there is more than just flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea... and ideas are bulletproof.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Alan Moore"},{"pid":"041a2a04754b57c7b7ff150dfab44c0cfbd4a621","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab437774f80c9854bd0cf379c23d0b362d72bc0","tid":1276791,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔覺喎"},{"pid":"b6d69d851c05b0ddf8199d62f039016e4e4da4f5","tid":1276791,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":49,"score":-49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"最多係1874， 定1984 定唔知咩"},{"pid":"99808711bd481e082f546f7843ef3ac46c19f4db","tid":1276791,"uid":26931,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"People should not be afraid of their government. <br />\n<br />\nGovernment should be afraid of their people."},{"pid":"f1f4474bf1ee224de2187e8c63543d62799f66ec","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"b6d69d851c05b0ddf8199d62f039016e4e4da4f5","tid":1276791,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":49,"score":-49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"最多係1874， 定1984 定唔知咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"1乜撚野874呀<br />\n瞓撚醒未呀"},{"pid":"b9a8e6eb46059cb2d3035d5fe882323bcb5cbd0a","tid":1276791,"uid":127952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"尋日政總真係見識到了 每個人都出一分力 我地要堅持落去 直到五大訴求成功為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d8182884f2e96c2e1131eba50c48063278a8c7","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"今鋪大家一定要all in 堅持撐落去"},{"pid":"7598801dd6955c961e3a0efe07c7f28355e89eed","tid":1276791,"uid":188546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"加油!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91184f2eab5b6c284fa977ed9da945b9e556007","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知由幾時開始<br />\n我覺得香港愈黎愈似 V 個世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0K17b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0K17b.jpg&h=73e246e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特別是近10幾年, 香港政權逐步逐步挑戰香港人嘅底線<br />\n由2003年廿三條開始，香港電視牌照風波，高鐵工程，第三條跑道，港珠澳大橋，國民教育，ＤＱ議員，，雨傘運動，魚蛋革命，鉛水事件，新界東北發展，中環海濱割地，沙中線醜聞。。。。。。。我數唔落去了<br />\n<br />\nＶ個世界，係極權統治下，係一個絕望無助嘅世界，充滿白色恐怖嘅世界，警察淪為政治工具，加上種種被嚴重鈕曲嘅價值觀，係一個典型嘅 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Dystopia</span></strong>。係一個冇人想要嘅世界。<br />\n<br />\n同現時嘅香港，我可以話係無分別。<br />\n<br />\n慶幸嘅係Ｖ世界裡面嘅人民覺醒，成功推倒一個腐敗嘅政權<br />\n我想講香港都好慶幸有一班辛辛學子喚醒左一班＂不了要返工＂，＂好攰咪搞＂，＂政治關我撚事＂嘅香港人，將 ６９，６１２，６１９，７１上演。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話Ｖ世界裡面多得Ｖ嘅出現，香港尚欠一個Ｖ<br />\n其實係香港，Ｖ早就出現了<br />\n佢係你嘅親人，佢係你嘅朋友，佢亦都係你嘅同事<br />\n佢係同你一齊發夢嘅每一位<br />\n佢係我地任何一個<br />\n<br />\n係Ｖ呢個咁黑暗嘅世界都有一絲曙光<br />\n我相信香港都有<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Behind this mask there is more than just flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea... and ideas are bulletproof.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Alan Moore</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8bba73b48671ba097a76db2ccda61140569f14f7","tid":1276791,"uid":15209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c137354f09c43e925c23850f53e1549e1aa6c822","tid":1276791,"uid":161222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b6d69d851c05b0ddf8199d62f039016e4e4da4f5","tid":1276791,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":49,"score":-49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"最多係1874， 定1984 定唔知咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"連書名都唔柒記得就google肯定先comment啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f379f43850445169705c2938529a4de6620d82c","tid":1276791,"uid":159913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b6d69d851c05b0ddf8199d62f039016e4e4da4f5","tid":1276791,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":49,"score":-49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"最多係1874， 定1984 定唔知咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"係1664呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">得閒唔該幫手推一下 等更多義士睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「長期置頂」夢遊後執手尾須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276769</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8ee06c42fbb0dde1c9eb3093e65eb80a8d21fccb","tid":1276791,"uid":164689,"like":1,"dislike":1,